{"tid":2375932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"玩coin master玩到冇晒同事親朋戚友......","createTime":"2021-01-22T11:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T15:29:33.000Z","uid":303864,"like":15,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a8e7d761f168efcfcd43a0f14967077d032236f","tid":2375932,"uid":303864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:40:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟最近玩緊隻coin master  咁琴晚因為攞琴到獎勵啲能量爆撚晒 我就襯啲人瞓緊覺補唔到盾將佢地啲村炸到完全得番灰為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每一個識既我都炸左一輪 炸到黑色一躂躂 爽能到high high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果今日番到公司同人打招呼完全冇人應我......我問佢地晏就食咩佢地都唔應我......最後發覺佢地趁我去廁所個時出嚟去......<br />\n<br />\n啱啱番到屋企發覺比自己大學group啲人踢左......我去左問個admin friend咩事佢藍剔左我.......<br />\n<br />\n我心知不妙去睇下facebook friend list發覺琴日炸左既二姑媽將我unfriend埋 之後新年都唔知點面對佢..........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家同冇玩既friend訴緊苦...點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1582f0c89fac93e72304b14a1c57f2f9fda11639","tid":2375932,"uid":131522,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:41:44.000Z","msg":"善心打破0回覆"},{"pid":"b5925bf6b0114f5676e0ea2f1cdabf7a4ad04bb7","tid":2375932,"uid":303864,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"1582f0c89fac93e72304b14a1c57f2f9fda11639","tid":2375932,"uid":131522,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:41:44.000Z","msg":"善心打破0回覆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:42:37.000Z","msg":"Po左一分鐘都冇洗撚你個廢柴覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9dded2d576e60144fd704037